data.description: Welcome to your stunning new 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home located in the beloved Hunter's Creek subdivision, NO CITY TAXES. Here you'll be part of a friendly community with easy access to local amenities, schools, and beaches. Plus, you're only a short drive away from base, and all the recreational opportunities NC has to offer. This is not just a house; it's an NC haven. With Carolina blue walls, a screened-in back porch, and ample space for entertaining. This home beautifully embodies the spirit of the Tar Heel State.The layout is thoughtfully designed, with a comfortable flow from room to room, ensuring that every corner of the house is functional and inviting.Whether you're hosting a dinner party or just enjoying a quiet night in, this home accommodates all your needs.The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances, ample counter space, and storage.Each of the four bedrooms offers plenty of comfort. Whether you're using them as guest rooms, or a home office these spaces cater to your lifestyle.Outside, the .84 acre lot is beautifully maintained and fully fenced, providing a secure space for children and pets to play.This home is more than just a property; it's a piece of North Carolina pride waiting for its new owners to call it their own. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful Carolina-inspired house your forever home. Contact today to schedule a viewing and experience the magic of this remarkable residence for yourself.
